#META# primaryLanguage: New Persian (Arabic script)
#META# documentType: Letter
#META# writingSupport: paper
#META# contentSummary: A short letter referred to as *khidmat*, from the residents of the village of Rām (?) to Shujāʿ al-Dawla wal-Dīn ʿAlī. The senders inform the recipient that their oxen are very weak and cannot come to the field, probably in order to plough the land. They therefore ask him to find another solution.
